parameters.query:
INSERT INTO business_processes_states (business_process_id, company_id,n8n_workflow_execution_id,n8n_workflow_root_execution_id, started)
SELECT MAX(business_process_id), $2,$3,$4, NOW()
FROM public.business_processes
WHERE n8n_process_name = $1;
update business_processes_states set finished=NOW() where business_process_id=(select MAX(business_process_id) from business_processes where n8n_process_name=$1) and n8n_workflow_execution_id=$2
update business_processes_states set steps_passed=$2, tokens_used=$3,tokens_used_type=$4 where n8n_workflow_execution_id=$1

parameters.query: update business_processes_states set steps_total=$3 where business_process_id=(select MAX(business_process_id) from business_processes where n8n_process_name=$1) and n8n_workflow_execution_id=$2

INSERT INTO public.company_name_variants (company_id, is_common_word, name_text, embedding, report_id)
VALUES ($1, false, $2, $3::vector, $4)
ON CONFLICT (company_id, name_text) DO NOTHING
RETURNING company_id, name_text;

SELECT
    cs.company_name,
    cs.company_url,
    string_agg(
        concat_ws(' ', serv.service_name, serv.service_description),
        ' '
    ) AS services_description
FROM companies cs
JOIN company_services serv
    ON cs.company_id = serv.company_id
WHERE cs.company_id = $1
GROUP BY
    cs.company_name,
    cs.company_url;
